ffef73c25293","tid":2396282,"uid":249170,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T03:13:12.000Z","msg":"女人結婚都係因為唔想俾個社會label做失敗者之嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n女人又唔可以好似男人咁一生放縱愛自由玩女玩到50歲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個世界有幾多個吳婉芳<br />\n<br />\n有吳婉芳咁既質素既女一早嫁左俾有錢佬啦<br />\n<br />\n洗鬼擔心年老色衰 冇錢 老公出軌 乜柒物柒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有返D自知之明既女一早嫁左人<br />\n<br />\n因為呢個社會始終會label嫁唔出既女 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果女有得好似仔咁出去流浪返十幾年覺得睇夠呢個世界先成家立室<br />\n<br />\n我諗唔會咁多女想早結婚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結婚對男女雙方都冇好處, 認真 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地話男人結左婚要做家庭ATM<br />\n<br />\n咁證明結婚對男人其實都冇好處 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"370f116f9ad4d880209fe22156536ce17f971088","tid":2396282,"uid":70192,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T03:16:49.000Z","msg":"其實點解離婚唔可以係女方比膳養費男方？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b304b1aefd7df31242df89810cd352e9a5428ea","tid":2396282,"uid":88033,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T03:20:05.000Z","msg":"咁你咪咪撚結婚囉 弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52fd6230bf6445266a330d835bef34e3dfac809d","tid":2396282,"uid":237459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T03:20:46.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"522aee353bd7c5c2d06cf23fa9b9afb51ff3260b","tid":2396282,"uid":129138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"370f116f9ad4d880209fe22156536ce17f971088","tid":2396282,"uid":70192,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T03:16:49.000Z","msg":"其實點解離婚唔可以係女方比膳養費男方？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\"